This project was initialized with [@relational-fabric/canon](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@relational-fabric/canon).

## Available Scripts

- `npm run check:all` — run linting, type checking, tests, and radar validation
- `npm run check:all:fix` — auto-fix lint issues then run the remaining checks
- `npm run dev` — watch the primary Canon entry point
- `npm run build:docs` — build documentation with VitePress
- `npm run build:adr` — generate ADR tables of contents and index files

Refer to Canon's documentation for deeper guidance on axioms, canons, and the curated toolkit.
